name: Programmer
description:
Our subconscious works on materializing our beliefs, it has no sense of humor, but it always does what we believe. We are the programmers of our destiny, as a species we believe so much in work and progress that, in this frantic search, the human species dug the ground, felled forests, awakened diseases and did not eradicate hunger. The programmer knows what we are, the programmer is you.
By glauberbnunes
https://linktr.ee/glauberbnunes
